Title: Living the life as a piece of art
DateModified: '2019-03-14'
DatePublished: '2019-03-14'
Url: https://www.worldnomads.com/create/scholarships/writing/2019/applications/living-the-life-as-a-piece-of-art
SetInCountry: Argentina
Category: A leap into the unknown
AuthorName: Mercedes  Vigo
AuthorCountry: Spain
Text: "My name is mercedes, i\u2019m 33 years old and I came to barcelona one year\
  \ and a half ago to study a master in art therapy, my story is about my self and\
  \ my question about life.\nI Travel to New Zealand when I was 25 years  it was the\
  \ first time I left my country to leaved and know a new places culture and practice\
  \ the language, then I went back home and spend some time saving money and searching\
  \ for the new destiny, in between I broke up with my boyfriend for 10 years and\
  \ open a new way or think the life... in that moment barcelona show me all the possibilities\
  \ to made my journey, I came here in 2017, started the master, travel to some countries\
  \ and Europe, work as a waitress, know a lot of people, and still want it more.\
  \ On July I finish my master and I want to travel the world exploring and showing\
  \ how I find the art in  the simple things of life."
